ad 类型**：必须使用 `shared-types` 中定义的 DTO/Interface，禁止内联 `any`\n   25
8\t\n   259\t   ```typescript\n   260\t   // ✅ 正确\n   261\t   import { MatchC
reatedEvent } from "@social-world/shared-types";\n   262\t   this.server.to(room
